text: Moslem Rostamiha (, born 18 June 1992) is an Iranian futsal player. He is a Left Winger, and currently a member of Setaregan Varamin. == Honours == === Country === === Club === * Iranian Futsal Super League ** Runners-up (1): 2015-16 (Mes Sungun) === Individual === * Best player: ** Best Young Player of the 2014–15 Iranian Futsal Super League مسلم رستمی‌ها بازیکن جوان سال ۹۳ شد (Mes Soongoun) * Top Goalscorer: ** Iranian Futsal Super League: 2014–15 (Mes Soongoun) (25) ==References== == External links == * Category:Iranian men's futsal players Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Gostaresh Foolad FSC players Category:Mes Sungun FSC players
